{"tid":40112,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"支國國債期貨價格跌停！","createTime":"2016-12-15T03:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T03:54:37.000Z","uid":58309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47831ad41994777be8919095f1c21c3f2f0ae918","tid":40112,"uid":58309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"共產黨係咪已經被（老破）破產😏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHK ToolBar\t本地兩岸                              <br />\n內地國債期貨價格跌停<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=912468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D912468&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=40aa0ba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=912468</a><br />\n<br />\n中國債市近期已持續受壓，加上美國聯儲局加息四分一厘，而且點陣圖暗示明年或加息三次，多於之前的預測，導致今早中國國債期貨暴跌，五年和十年期國債期貨價格跌停，十年期國債跌百分之二觸及跌停板，是上市以來最大跌幅。在內地債災拖累下，中資金融股受壓，工商銀行(<a href=\"http://01398.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01398.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d05d751f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01398.HK</a>)、建設銀行(<a href=\"http://00939.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00939.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=2862cad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00939.HK</a>)和中國銀行(<a href=\"http://03988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03988.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e4e4bda2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03988.HK</a>)，跌百分之二，工行報4.58元，建行報5.58元，國壽(<a href=\"http://02628.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02628.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7224f108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02628.HK</a>)跌百分之三，報20.8元。"}]}